Flip our meat for us.

2607
01:27:21,436 --> 01:27:23,406
Don't you think it's done? Look at the edges.

2608
01:27:23,706 --> 01:27:25,876
You pig. Don't just eat and flip the meat.

2609
01:27:26,176 --> 01:27:28,345
