- I'll order mulnaengmyeon.
- Mulnaengmyeon.

2614
01:27:36,726 --> 01:27:38,602
- Ma'am, one mulnaengmyeon, please.
- One mulnaengmyeon, please.

2615
01:27:38,626 --> 01:27:40,125
- One mulnaengmyeon, please.
- One mulnaengmyeon, please.

2616
01:27:40,126 --> 01:27:42,026
