2678
01:29:52,656 --> 01:29:56,166
It's unbelievable that we're eating beef at this speed.

2679
01:29:56,266 --> 01:29:58,365
- It doesn't make sense.
- I know. I'm having a great time.

2680
01:29:58,366 --> 01:29:59,366
